    <description><![CDATA[ Caterpillar (working name) is a small, BLE-controlled vibrotactile board: an nRF54L15 module driving a vibration motor through a DRV8212 H-bridge and an STBB1-APUR boost rail, with an ASM330 IMU and a MAX5419 digital potentiometer that sets the motor voltage. ]]></description>
